data.title: Brace Face Wooden Nickels, Wooden Nickels: Office Easel Promotions
data.meta_description:
These real hardwood nickels make a wonderful patient incentive program. Develop your own system for patients to earn the tokens to let them purchase fun items like bottles, bags, gift cards, etc. The possibilities are endless! 
Made from real hardwood maple
Grown and milled in the USA
Measures 1.5 in diameter
One color Imprint - Black ink standard
Other colors available for $15
Copy change available for $20
Wooden nickels are sold in units of 500
data.text:
Imprint Area: 1.25" diameter

Allow 10 production days after art approval

Artwork for custom logos and messages can be emailed to artwork@officeeasel.com

When sending artwork please include: office name, address, and phone number. Please include the office name or order number (if available) in the subject line.

Preferred file formats (please remember to convert all fonts to outlines or embed them in the file):

PDF for pre-press

EPS - Encapsulated Postscript

Illustrator - CS2 or earlier

CDR - Corel Draw X3 or earlier

Other file formats accepted (these may incur a $20 art charge if artwork needs to be redrawn):

JPG - Joint Photographic Experts Group

TIF - Tagged Image File

BMP - Bitmap
